                        </t:graphic>
                     </t:figure>22 Mss. photographed: <t:ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/ESsqmm001">SQMM-001</t:ref> “Miracles of Mary”; <t:ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/ESsqmm002">SQMM-002</t:ref> “Homily on the Saviour of the World ”; <t:ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/ESsqmm003">SQMM-003</t:ref> “Mracles of Mary, The Prayer of Mary on the Mount Golgotha etc”; <t:ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/ESsqmm004">SQMM-004</t:ref> “The Rite of the Holy Week”; <t:ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/ESsqmm005">SQMM-005</t:ref> “Synaxarion (Mäggabit- Pägwǝmen)”; <t:ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/ESsqmm006">SQMM-006</t:ref> “Synaxarion (September-February)”; <t:ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/ESsqmm007">SQMM-007</t:ref> “Homily on St. Michael”; <t:ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/ESsqmm008">SQMM-008</t:ref> “Missal”; <t:ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/ESsqmm009">SQMM-009</t:ref> “Missal”; <t:ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/ESsqmm010">SQMM-010</t:ref> “Psalter of Dawit”; <t:ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/ESsqmm011">SQMM-011</t:ref> “Prayer of Incense”; <t:ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/ESsqmm012">SQMM-012</t:ref> “Miracles of Jesus”; <t:ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/ESsqmm013">SQMM-013</t:ref> “The Book of the Story of the Trinity”; <t:ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/ESsqmm014">SQMM-014</t:ref> “The Book of the Matrimony Rite”; <t:ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/ESsqmm015">SQMM-015</t:ref> “The Book of the Chants”; <t:ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/ESsqmm016">SQMM-016</t:ref> “The Book of Baptism”; <t:ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/ESsqmm017">SQMM-017</t:ref> “Psalter of Dawit”; <t:ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/ESsqmm018">SQMM-018</t:ref> “Dǝggwa”; <t:ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/ESsqmm019">SQMM-019</t:ref> “The Book of Ziq”; <t:ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/ESsqmm020">SQMM-020</t:ref> “Synoptic Lectionary for the Year”; <t:ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/ESsqmm021">SQMM-021</t:ref> “Deggwa, the Book of Qedär”; <t:ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/ESsqmm022">SQMM-022</t:ref> “Antiphonary”.</t:ab>
       
